hadiths[13]{hadithnumber,text}:
1224,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi (chaar rak'at) Namaz ki 2 rakaat padhaaney ke baad) Qada tashahud ke baghair ( khadey ho gaey, pahlaa Qada nahi kya. isliye log bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khadey ho gaey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz poori kar chukey to ham salam pherney ka intizar karne lagey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam se pahley baithey baithey ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur salam hi se pahley 2 sajdey baithey baithey kiye phir salam phera ."
1225,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki 2 rakaat padhney ke baad baithey baghair khadey ho gaey aur pahla Qada nahi kya, jab Namaz poori kar chukey to 2 sajdey kiye, phir unke baad salam phera ."
1226,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar mein panch rakaat padh liin. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kya Namaz ki rakatein zyada ho gaee hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya baat hai? kehney waley ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne panch rakatein padhi hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam ke baad 2 sajdey kiye.
1227,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ya Asr ki Namaz padhai jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to zul-yadain kehney laga ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya Namaz ki rakatein kam ho gaee hain? (kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhool kar sirf 2 rakaton par salam pher diya tha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab se malum kya ke kya ye sach kehtey hain? sahaba ne kaha ji haan, us ne sahi kaha hai. tab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat aur padhaaein phir 2 sajdey kiye. Sad ne bayan kya ke Urwa-bin-Zubair ko maine dekha ke aap ne maghrib ki 2 rakatein padh kar salam pher diya aur baatein bhi kin. phir baqi aik rakaat padhi aur 2 sajdey kiye aur farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya tha."
1228,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakaat padh kar uth khadey huey to zul-yadain ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! kya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se puchha ke kya zul-yadain sach kehtey hain. logon ne kaha ji haan ! ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur 2 rakaat jo reh gaee thin unko padha , phir salam phera , phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur apne sajdey ki tarah (yani Namaz ke maamooli sajdey ki tarah) sajda kya ya us se lamba phir sar uthaya ."
1229,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesrey pahar ki 2 namazon (zuhar ya asr) mein se koi Namaz padhi. mera ghalib guman ye hai ke wo Asr hi ki Namaz thi. usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sirf 2 hi rakaat par salam pher diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik darakht ke taney se jo masjid ki agli saf mein tha, tek laga kar khadey ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath is par rakhey huey they. haaziriin mein Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they lekin unhein bhi kuchh kehney ki himmat nahi hui. jo (jald baaz qism ke) log Namaz padhtey hi masjid se nikal janey ke aadi they. wo bahar ja chukey they. logon ne kaha kya Namaz ki rakatein kam ho gaiin. aik shakhs jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zul-yadain kehtey they. wo boley ya Rasulullah! aap bhool gaey ya Namaz mein kami ho gaii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya na main bhula hun aur na Namaz ki rakatein kam huin. zul-yadain boley ke nahi aap bhool gaey hain. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat aur padhi aur salam phera phir takbeer kahi aur mamool (routine) ke mutabiq ya usse bhi lamba sajda kya. jab sajde se sar uthaya to phir takbeer kahi aur phir takbeer keh kar sajde mein gaey. ye sajda bhi mamool (routine) ki tarah ya us se lamba tha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar uthaya aur takbeer kahi."
1230,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz mein pahla Qada kiye baghair khadey ho gaey. halanke us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baithna chahiye tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz poori ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baithey baithey hi salam se pahley 2 sajdey saho ke kiye aur har sajdey mein) Allahu-akbar ( kaha, muqtadiyon ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ye 2 sajdey kiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithna bhool gaey they, isliye ye sajdey usi ke badle mein kiye they. is riwayat ki mutaabia't (pairvi) ibne-juraij ne ibne-Shahab se takbeer ke zikr mein ki hai."
1231,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz ke liye azan hoti hai to shaitan hawa khaarij karta hua bhaagta hai taake azan na suney , jab azan poori ho jati hai to phir aa jata hai. jab iqamat hoti hai to phir bhag padta hai. lekin iqamat khatm hotey hi phir aa jata hai aur namazi ke dil mein tarah-tarah ke waswasey daalta hai aur kehta hai ke falan-falan baat yad karo, is tarah usey wo baatein yad dilata hai jo uske zahan mein nahi thin. lekin dusri taraf namazi ko ye bhi yad nahi rehta ke kitni rakatein us ne padhi hain. isliye agar kisi ko ye yad na rahe ke teen rakaat padhein ya char to baithey hi baithey saho ke 2 sajdey kar ley."
1232,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se jab koi Namaz padhney ke liye khada hota hai to shaitan aa kar uski Namaz mein shuba paida kar deta hai phir usey ye bhi yad nahi rehta ke kitni rakatein padhin. tum mein se jab kisi ko aisa ittifaq ho to baithey-baithey 2 sajdey kar ley.
1233,"ibne-Abbaas, miswar-bin-Makhrima aur Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Azhar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bheja aur kaha Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ham sab ka salam kehna aur uske baad Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaton ke barey mein malum karna. unhein ye bhi bata dena ke hamein khabar hui hai ke aap ye 2 rakatein padhti hain. halanke hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis pahunchi hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un 2 rakaton se mana kya hai aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath un rakaton ke padhney par logon ko maara bhi tha. Kureb ne bayan kya ke main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur paigham pahunchaayaa. iska jawab aap ne ye diya ke Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se iske mutaalliq malum kar. chunanche main un hazraat ki khidmat mein wapas hua aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki guftgu naql kar di, unhon-ne mujhey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bhejaa, unhein paighaamaat ke sath jinke sath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan bheja tha. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne ye jawab diya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ke baad Namaz padhney se roktey they lekin aik din maine dekha ke Asr ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud ye 2 rakatein padh rahe hain. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar tashrif laey. mere paas Ansar ke qabila bano haram ki chand auratein baithi hui thin. isliye maine aik baandi ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. maine us se keh diya tha ke wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bazu mein ho kar ye poochhey ke Umme-Salma kehti hain ke ya Rasulullah! aap to un 2 rakaton se mana kya kartey they halanke main dekh rahi hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud unhein padhtey hain. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hath se ishara karein to tum peechhey hat jaanaa. baandi ne phir isi tarah kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath se ishara kya to peechhey hat gaee. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh huey to (aap ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se) farmaya ke aey abu-Umaiya ki beti ! tum ne Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaton ke mutaalliq poochha, baat ye hai ke mere paas abdul-Qais ke kuchh log aagey they aur unke sath baat karne mein main Zohar ke baad ki 2 rakatein nahi padh saka tha so ye wahi 2 rakaat hain."
1234,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar pahunchi ke bani Amr-bin-Auf ke logon mein aapasii koi jhagdaa paida ho gaya hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chand sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath milaap karaaney ke liye wahan tashrif ley gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi mashghool hi they ke Namaz ka waqt ho gaya. isliye Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi tak tashrif nahi laey. idhar Namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai. kya aap logon ki imamat karengey ? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, agar tum chaho . chunanche Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne takbeer kahi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aagey badh kar takbeer ( tahreema ( kahi . itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi safon se guzartey huey pehli saf mein aa kar khadey ho gaey. logon ne ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aagah karne ke liye) hath par hath bajaaney shuru kar diye lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein kisi taraf dhyaan nahi diya kartey they. jab logon ne bahut taaliyaan bajaaiin to aap mutwajjeh huey aur kya dekhtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaare se unhein Namaz padhatey rehney ke liye kaha, is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hath utha kar Allah Taala ka shukr ada kya aur ultey paon peechhey ki taraf aa kar saf mein khadey ho gaey phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aagey badh kar Namaz padhai. Namaz ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, logo ! Namaz mein aik Amr pesh aaya to tum log hath par hath kyon maarney lagey they, ye dastak dena to sirf aurton ke liye hai. jis ko Namaz mein koi haadisa pesh aaey to (Sub'haanallah) kahey kyonke jab bhi koi (sub'haanallah) sunega wo idhar khayal karega aur aey abu-Bakar! mere ishaarey ke bawajud tum logon ko Namaz kyon nahi padhatey rahe? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke bhala abu-Qahaafa ke betey ki kya majaal thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey Namaz padhaaey."
1235,main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaee. us waqt wo khadi Namaz padh rahi thin. log bhi khadey Namaz padh rahe they. maine puchha ke kya baat huii? to unhon-ne sar se aasman ki taraf ishara kya. maine puchha ke kya koi nishani hai? to unhon-ne apne sar ke ishaarey se kaha ke haan.
1236,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar they. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghar hi mein baith kar Namaz padhi logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey ho kar Namaz padhi. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein baithney ka ishara kya aur Namaz ke baad farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. isliye jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthaao.
